CustomField.description: This field was requested by the Partner Relations and College Counseling teams. It indicates the type of pathway a student can follow for guaranteed admission to the channel partner school. The pathway may be guaranteed no matter what (Spring Start), or guaranteed only after successful completion of a Verto semester (Scholars).
